================================================================================
Plotting utility programs
================================================================================
To plot runtime statistics the user can use a bunch of GNUplot-Python scripts.
The corresponding folder must be copied as is in the same directory of the test 
case where Log Data and Fig folders mst also be present.
Compatibility issues: GNUplot 4.0 and 4.2 versions.

To plot in paraFoam the structural deformation of an aero-elastic wing the user
can use the post-processing utility showDisplacement which moves the mesh.
